The paper discusses the use of artificial immune systems in network security, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of artificial intelligence in the implementation of these systems, which suggests the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the challenges and prototype implementation of the system, which suggests the categories of network and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), and software engineering (cs.SE).
